body:
I was able to make a workaround by adding correct import in TensorProtosDBInput. 
```
%%bash
sed -i '454 c\
        from caffe2.python.helpers.db_input import db_input\
        return db_input(' /opt/caffe2/caffe2/python/model_helper.py
```
